      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p "> In the case the battery solution is not included
with the system solution all wiring up to the terminal needs to be
done by the customer before the installation of the system. The fuse/MCCB
protection for the battery might be still be included in the offer.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">When connecting the batteries consider that:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">All wiring must comply with all applicable local and/or national
electrical codes</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The cables and connections are installed according to the drawings,
see the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Circuit Diagram</i>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The required fuse/MCCB protection is installed according to
the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Technical Data</i>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The person carrying out the work must be an authorized electrician.</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
